{"name":"页面开发","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/categories/%E9%A1%B5%E9%9D%A2%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91/","url":"/async/categories/页面开发.json","count":16,"_total":16,"_totalPage":2,"_page":1,"posts":[{"tags":[{"name":"CSS","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/tags/CSS/","url":"/async/tags/CSS.json","count":21}],"categories":[{"name":"页面开发","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/categories/%E9%A1%B5%E9%9D%A2%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91/","url":"/async/categories/页面开发.json","count":16}],"url":"/async/posts/2014/02/26/old/BFC.json","date":1393344000000,"path":{"year":2014,"month":2,"day":26,"name":"old/BFC"},"subtitle":"什么是BFC？它如何出现、又干了些什么？","title":"深入浅出BFC（Block formatting contexts）","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/2014/02/26/old/BFC/","content":"<p>BFC（Block formatting contexts）,是W3C CSS 2.1中的一个概念，决定了元素如何对其内容进行定位，以及与其他元素的关系和相互作用。在创建了BFC的元素中，子元素会一个接一个的被放置…</p>"},{"tags":[{"name":"CSS","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/tags/CSS/","url":"/async/tags/CSS.json","count":21}],"categories":[{"name":"页面开发","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/categories/%E9%A1%B5%E9%9D%A2%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91/","url":"/async/categories/页面开发.json","count":16}],"url":"/async/posts/2014/02/25/old/css-selectors-priority.json","date":1393257600000,"path":{"year":2014,"month":2,"day":25,"name":"old/css-selectors-priority"},"subtitle":"记录CSS优先级计算的规则，再也不用害怕面试官问了","title":"CSS优先级备忘","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/2014/02/25/old/css-selectors-priority/","content":""},{"tags":[{"name":"CSS","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/tags/CSS/","url":"/async/tags/CSS.json","count":21}],"categories":[{"name":"页面开发","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/categories/%E9%A1%B5%E9%9D%A2%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91/","url":"/async/categories/页面开发.json","count":16}],"url":"/async/posts/2014/03/07/old/display.json","date":1394121600000,"path":{"year":2014,"month":3,"day":7,"name":"old/display"},"subtitle":"通过实例对比display的block、inline、inline-block属性","title":"对比display布局（clearfix）","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/2014/03/07/old/display/","content":"<p>最近在看面试题的时候看到很多次出现display的inline、block、inline-block的区别。在这里做一做实验，可以从margin、padding、border、width、height来区别</p>"},{"tags":[{"name":"CSS","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/tags/CSS/","url":"/async/tags/CSS.json","count":21},{"name":"HTML","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/tags/HTML/","url":"/async/tags/HTML.json","count":17}],"categories":[{"name":"页面开发","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/categories/%E9%A1%B5%E9%9D%A2%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91/","url":"/async/categories/页面开发.json","count":16}],"url":"/async/posts/2014/05/21/old/google-adding-interactivity-with-javaScript.json","date":1400601600000,"path":{"year":2014,"month":5,"day":21,"name":"old/google-adding-interactivity-with-javaScript"},"subtitle":"翻译自谷歌Web开发最佳实践手册","title":"通过JavaScript增加交互性","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/2014/05/21/old/google-adding-interactivity-with-javaScript/","content":"<p>JavaScript允许我们网页中的几乎所有的部分：网页内容、样式等等，它还能提供用户交互的行为。然而，JavaScript也会在页面被渲染时阻塞和延迟DOM树的构建。保证JavaScript代码的异步性，删除不必要的JavaScript代码，可以优化性能。</p>"},{"tags":[{"name":"CSS","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/tags/CSS/","url":"/async/tags/CSS.json","count":21},{"name":"HTML","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/tags/HTML/","url":"/async/tags/HTML.json","count":17}],"categories":[{"name":"页面开发","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/categories/%E9%A1%B5%E9%9D%A2%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91/","url":"/async/categories/页面开发.json","count":16}],"url":"/async/posts/2014/05/21/old/google-measuring-the-critical-rendering-path-with-navigation-timing.json","date":1400601600000,"path":{"year":2014,"month":5,"day":21,"name":"old/google-measuring-the-critical-rendering-path-with-navigation-timing"},"subtitle":"翻译自谷歌Web开发最佳实践手册","title":"使用导航计时监测渲染关键路径","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/2014/05/21/old/google-measuring-the-critical-rendering-path-with-navigation-timing/","content":"<p>没办法监测，就没办法优化。幸运的是，浏览器提供了一系列用来监测渲染关键路径上每一步的接口，叫导航计时接口（Navigation Timing API）</p>"},{"tags":[{"name":"JavaScript","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/tags/JavaScript/","url":"/async/tags/JavaScript.json","count":26},{"name":"前端架构","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/tags/%E5%89%8D%E7%AB%AF%E6%9E%B6%E6%9E%84/","url":"/async/tags/前端架构.json","count":3}],"categories":[{"name":"页面开发","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/categories/%E9%A1%B5%E9%9D%A2%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91/","url":"/async/categories/页面开发.json","count":16}],"url":"/async/posts/2014/05/03/old/javascript-mvc.json","date":1399046400000,"path":{"year":2014,"month":5,"day":3,"name":"old/javascript-mvc"},"subtitle":"简要介绍MVC、MVP和MVVM架构模式之间的异同","title":"JavaScript的MV*模式","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/2014/05/03/old/javascript-mvc/","content":"<p>虽然在做J2EE的时候就已经对MVC有一定的了解，但平常经常听到的MVVM和MVP模式却完全无法理解是什么意思，《JavaScript设计模式》一书中对MVC、MVP、MVVM做了一个详尽的解释，这里记录了一下上面的知识并做了一个简述，正好在学Angular，这些知识结合Angular一起也更加清晰具体了</p>"},{"tags":[{"name":"CSS","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/tags/CSS/","url":"/async/tags/CSS.json","count":21}],"categories":[{"name":"页面开发","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/categories/%E9%A1%B5%E9%9D%A2%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91/","url":"/async/categories/页面开发.json","count":16}],"url":"/async/posts/2014/02/09/old/box-shadow-pix-image.json","date":1391875200000,"path":{"year":2014,"month":2,"day":9,"name":"old/box-shadow-pix-image"},"subtitle":"使用CSS3属性box-shadow，绘制超级玛丽","title":"使用box-shadow绘制像素画","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/2014/02/09/old/box-shadow-pix-image/","content":"<p>曾经在codepen.io上看到很多像素画，都是css3实现的，点进去看才知道是使用box-shadow实现的，但是当时并不了解CSS3的box-shadow属性。如今稍微了解了box-shadow属性，并自己绘制了一个超级玛丽</p>"},{"tags":[{"name":"CSS","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/tags/CSS/","url":"/async/tags/CSS.json","count":21},{"name":"HTML","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/tags/HTML/","url":"/async/tags/HTML.json","count":17}],"categories":[{"name":"页面开发","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/categories/%E9%A1%B5%E9%9D%A2%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91/","url":"/async/categories/页面开发.json","count":16}],"url":"/async/posts/2014/05/04/old/google-style-guide.json","date":1399132800000,"path":{"year":2014,"month":5,"day":4,"name":"old/google-style-guide"},"subtitle":"写更简洁、更美观的HTML和CSS","title":"Google的HTML/CSS样式指南","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/2014/05/04/old/google-style-guide/","content":"<p>之前读过网易的NEC，以及百度的前端编码规范，感觉自己HTML和CSS代码写的很烂，这里又读了一下Google的style guide，发现有很多地方值得学习补充，在这里大致上翻译一下</p>"},{"tags":[{"name":"JavaScript","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/tags/JavaScript/","url":"/async/tags/JavaScript.json","count":26},{"name":"语言特性","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/tags/%E8%AF%AD%E8%A8%80%E7%89%B9%E6%80%A7/","url":"/async/tags/语言特性.json","count":4}],"categories":[{"name":"页面开发","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/categories/%E9%A1%B5%E9%9D%A2%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91/","url":"/async/categories/页面开发.json","count":16}],"url":"/async/posts/2014/03/28/old/js-basis.json","date":1395936000000,"path":{"year":2014,"month":3,"day":28,"name":"old/js-basis"},"subtitle":"作用域链、原型链、闭包、UI线程","title":"JavaScript一些基础知识简介","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/2014/03/28/old/js-basis/","content":"<p>最近看笔试面试题时，总是看到问这些JavaScript基础知识，所以在这里总结了一下原型链、作用域链、闭包和UI线程的知识基础，希望以后问到的时候能答得上来</p>"},{"tags":[{"name":"CSS","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/tags/CSS/","url":"/async/tags/CSS.json","count":21}],"categories":[{"name":"页面开发","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/categories/%E9%A1%B5%E9%9D%A2%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91/","url":"/async/categories/页面开发.json","count":16}],"url":"/async/posts/2014/03/31/old/css-layout.json","date":1396195200000,"path":{"year":2014,"month":3,"day":31,"name":"old/css-layout"},"subtitle":"包含块、浮动、相对定位、绝对定位以及布局属性相关关系","title":"CSS布局相关基础知识","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/2014/03/31/old/css-layout/","content":""}]}